IRS990EZ.PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt: CHI OMEGA IS A SISTERHOOD THAT PROVIDES A NETWORK OF FRIENDS AND LIFELONG DEVELOPMENT FOR COLLEGIATE AND ALUMNAE MEMBERS, COMMITTED TO PERSONAL INTEGRITY, EXCELLENCE IN ACADEMIC AND INTELLECTUAL PURSUITS, INTER-GENERATIONAL PARTICIPATION, COMMUNITY SERVICE, LEADERSHIP OPPORTUNITIES, AND SOCIAL ENRICHMENT.CHI OMEGA'S VISION IS TO BE THE PREMIER NATIONAL WOMEN'S ORGANIZATION IN THE 21ST CENTURY AND TO ESTABLISH RENEWED VALUE AND RESPECT FOR ALL WOMEN BY PROMOTING 1)HIGH MORAL STANDARDS AND ETHICS, 2) PERSONAL GROWTH, 3) PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT, AND 4) A NETWORK OF FRIENDSHIP AND SUPPORT FOR LIFE.
